TITLE: Using Custom Backoff Strategy in Job Configuration in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to add a job that uses a previously defined custom backoff strategy. The job is configured to make up to 3 retry attempts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/taskforcesh/bullmq/blob/master/docs/gitbook/guide/retrying-failing-jobs.md#2025-04-14_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { Queue } from 'bullmq';

const myQueue = new Queue('foo');

